description:
Beauty influencer Arshia Moorjani pulls back the curtain on what it's like to be a full-time content creator, how she is trying to elevate the space, and the beauty dupe she swears by. Before that: We talk about semi-permanent makeup; derm-designed haircare; and how your next shower can help change someone's world. Really.
